The paper proposes a privacy-preserving machine learning model and a secure cross-regional machine learning system, which are related to topics in machine learning (cs.LG), data privacy and security (cs.CR), data management (cs.DB), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of random forest method also suggests a possible connection to data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
